Cassandra Magrath https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cassandra_Magrath 0 Cassandra Magrath (born 8 January 1981 in Melbourne) is an Australian actress. She played Miranda Gibson in the Australian ABC 1998–2000 television series SeaChange and Liz Hunter in the 2005 Australian horror film Wolf Creek.
